{"tid":1543610,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"831 太子站真相 - 各方證供集合區","createTime":"2019-09-05T08:55:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T12:34:09.000Z","uid":52152,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a353326d2773df556b699ec6d3984054eb8b135d","tid":1543610,"uid":52152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T08:55:16.000Z","msg":"831 太子站發生恐怖襲擊既事件令到好多香港人憤怒，不安，除咗之外依件事帶黎既係疑惑。究竟成件事既真相係點？因為出面有好多個唔同既post 講緊唔同方面既論述，所以希望大家可以將唔同既論述集中討論分析。<br />\n<br />\n對事件有關既人：狗，黨鐵，香港人權，記者，救護人員<br />\n<br />\n官方論述：<br />\n<br />\n一開始：10個傷者，7個送院<br />\n依家：數錯數，只有7個傷者<br />\n<br />\n香港人權監察<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=3118284291576578&amp;id=396923137046054\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D3118284291576578%26id%3D396923137046054&d=g6cJT0UyhZ9RanxftZ%2B8MPrL6OgrijQqmkkA1x3Ej7w%3D&h=3c37d5e7\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=3118284291576578&amp;id=396923137046054</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄：<br />\n由於兩名觀察員不欲被迫回到地面結束在太子站的觀察，故走回車廂試圖繼續觀察，<span style=\"color: red;\">但列車竟然關門開行，把尚留在車廂的數十乘客載至石硤尾</span>，然後才停止列車服務。當晚，位於太子站鄰近的觀察員，也再無法進入太子站。<br />\n<br />\n個人意見：文中所指既列車應該係揸鎚藍絲既車<br />\n<br />\n[未能證實]連登疑似手足既post<br />\n原post 未有時間搵，但係內容大慨係手足架車係離開太子月台後停係隧道入面，一行人需要<span style=\"color: red;\">沿路軌逃生，經過深水埗，長沙灣，荔枝角站逃出不果，最後行到美孚站先可以爆門逃生</span><br />\n<br />\n個人意見：由直播睇到有列車係成功開出，狗仔發現大叫『停車』並嘗試按下月台緊急停車制剎停列車，但列車仍然離開左直播既鏡頭。剎停既機制未明(睇下有冇地鐵巴解釋) 但係如果post內容係真既，估計就係依班車，出左月台後被剎停。如果要證實既話，我諗到既係美孚站向荃灣方向月台車尾既CCTV，雖然黨鐵未必公開，但係如果以post所講要爆門逃生既話，車尾既幕門應該有被破壞既痕跡<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望大家可以幫手分析下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d00883422e0cfd5dc81f5f233be85a0a6296927d","tid":1543610,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T08:55:28.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fefc477cce9506917796dc13d7c412f62362f0b0","tid":1543610,"uid":211578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T09:04:51.000Z","msg":"6月9撤回同9月4撤回分別係邊呀?<br />\n分別在於：<br />\n<br />\n殉港手足：<br />\n梁凌杰先生（35歲） - 15/6/2019<br />\n盧曉欣小姐（21歲） - 30/6/2019<br />\nZhita Wu（29歲） - 30/6/2019<br />\n麥小姐（28歲） - 3/7/2019<br />\n梅先生（32歲） - 5/7/2019<br />\n范先生（26歲） - 22/7/2019<br />\nCalvin 郭先生（25歲） - 27/8/2019<br />\n姬先生（16歲） - 2/9/2019 <br />\n何小姐（27歲） - 4/9/2019<br />\n9人離世<br />\n<br />\n還有：<br />\n4隻眼<br />\n2次地鐵恐襲<br />\n2人被刀手斬至重傷<br />\n超過100人被檢控<br />\n超過1000人被捕<br />\n受傷, 逃亡不計其數<br />\n<br />\n淨係計以上的分別, 已經好明顯。<br />\n還有整個警隊及制度的不公義已暴露。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OkC3deC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOkC3deC.jpg&h=34367fd0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D2LPVhj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD2LPVhj.jpg&h=35c3dac3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C4TBAhk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC4TBAhk.jpg&h=05bdd3d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8udugLx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8udugLx.jpg&h=bae3ed34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0ZTBFS9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0ZTBFS9.jpg&h=3e1d2264&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《願榮光歸香港》<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/y7yRDOLCy4Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fy7yRDOLCy4Y&d=g6cJT0UyhZ9RanxftZ%2B8MPrL6OgrijQqmkkA1x3Ej7w%3D&h=7766284a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/y7yRDOLCy4Y</a>"},{"pid":"908ea270761cc8f06a4e9c24bb487ead55d4d975","tid":1543610,"uid":303830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T09:08:46.000Z","msg":"件事8月31日發生，9月4日消防署先岀嚟話數錯數？8月31日當晚已經開始有人懷疑死左人，要隔咁多日先知數錯數？係咪用左呢幾日嚟令到條數啱番曬？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190904/s00001/1567603251439/%E3%80%90%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-831%E3%80%91%E7%B6%B2%E5%82%B3%E5%A4%AA%E5%AD%90%E7%AB%9910%E5%82%B7%E8%80%85%E4%B8%AD3%E4%BA%BA%E3%80%8C%E6%B6%88%E5%A4%B1%E3%80%8D-%E6%B6%88%E9%98%B2%E8%99%95-%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%E6%AC%A1%E9%BB%9E%E7%AE%97%E7%A2%BA%E8%AA%8D7%E4%BA%BA%E9%80%81%E9%99%A2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190904%2Fs00001%2F1567603251439%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B-831%25E3%2580%2591%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E5%2582%25B3%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E5%25AD%2590%25E7%25AB%259910%25E5%2582%25B7%25E8%2580%2585%25E4%25B8%25AD3%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E3%2580%258C%25E6%25B6%2588%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E3%2580%258D-%25E6%25B6%2588%25E9%2598%25B2%25E8%2599%2595-%25E7%25AC%25AC%25E4%25BA%258C%25E6%25AC%25A1%25E9%25BB%259E%25E7%25AE%2597%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25AA%258D7%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%2580%2581%25E9%2599%25A2&d=g6cJT0UyhZ9RanxftZ%2B8MPrL6OgrijQqmkkA1x3Ej7w%3D&h=3b5aa2b6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190904%2Fs00001%2F1567603251439%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B-831%25E3%2580%2591%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E5%2582%25B3%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E5%25AD%2590%25E7%25AB%259910%25E5%2582%25B7%25E8%2580%2585%25E4%25B8%25A